divs: Sighting DetailsObject was traveling straight then did an abrupt turn and went bact the way it first was traveling from moving very slowly , red lights on each end pulsated in unison , that is how we could tell it was one long object, much too big to be a plane or helicopter maybe 100 yards or longer. Object was observed until it was out of sight. Was seen by appropriate 5 people, got some video and a few photos, but have not looked at them and am not sure if anything will show up yet.
Summary: long with red lights on each end that blinked or pulsated in unison
